+    # ------------------------------------------------------------------
+    # write_file — chunked-upload-aware (fixes A.2 silent truncation)
+    # ------------------------------------------------------------------
+
+    # Threshold above which we route writes through NC chunked-upload v2.
+    # NC's PHP layer typically caps single PUT at php.ini upload_max_filesize
+    # (2M default; many installs raise to 8M-128M). MCP transport may cap
